title: Ju Chong Gongyuan
synopsis: The three children boarded a cruise ship during the summer vacation. During the voyage, they were taken away from the ship by unknown creatures and fell on a deserted island in the middle of the vast sea. This mysterious island is full of unusually huge species of plants and animals. The huge insects are the main occupants of the island and the biggest threat to children. In order to escape from the isolated island and return to civilized society, the three children carried out a series of self-rescue actions, fought continuously in nature, and escaped from the mouth of giant insects several times. During the period, she frequently encountered an aboriginal girl whose whereabouts were uncertain and her friends and enemies were indistinguishable. With the deepening of the thrilling escape journey of three urban teenagers and indigenous girls, various mysteries that have been obscured by dense forests on the isolated island for several centuries are also revealed. The film is based on the story of three children participating in a summer camp at sea. The characters are cute, the imagination is rich, the story is climax, and the production is skillful. It is highly educational and informative. It conforms to the psychological characteristics of children and can see the big from the small. Enlighten and educate people!(translated from douban)

To live in such a harsh environment, courage alone is far from enough, but optimism, optimism, optimism, optimism and important things are said four times. He quickly became famous for his wisdom, and thieves shunned it. As a result, under his prestige, Xiaohai has to solve more and more things, and the problems he encounters become more and more strange. When he was exhausted, he luckily ran into another young wizard--little girl Lala. They became partners and companions, defending the pure land of Mount Jiuhua together, circling among the knights and thieves all day long, playing the game of "cat and mouse", and the thieves and friends; the obscurity between them Feelings, interpretation of endless stories. As a result, Pan Bai wounded the minister, took away the white cat queen's moon phantom star, and imprisoned her. He used the energy of the phantom star to open the black hole leading to the planet Sembolo, preparing to invade Sembolo. At this time, Sembolo was in peace, Bodhi was riding a skateboard and taking the alien life detector to the mountain top park for experiments. On the way, I ran into a motorcyclist who deliberately played tricks on Bodhi. Bodhi turned them around. The motorcyclist's car almost hit a child, but Bodhi, who responded quickly, saved the child. The drag racing clan couldn't control the car that rushed to the cliff. Bodhi stabilized the speeding car at the very moment, and then drove the speeding car towards the city center. The speeding car was speeding through the buildings in the city center and was about to hit the building. Bodhi Jizhong Shengzhi drove the speeding car to the weightless experience hall on the top floor of the Greentown Science and Technology Museum, avoiding an accident. Afterwards, Bodhi went to the Peak Park on the top of the Green City to conduct experiments. Sure enough, the alien life detector detected the alien race! Although the powerful energy impact caused by this caused the detector to be destroyed. But Bodhi was very happy, because he proved his conjecture-there are indeed alien creatures in this world.(translated from douban)

Unexpectedly, the head of prisoners, Stason, turned Moon City upside down, but the Space Rat got involved in several hapless disputes between the "Alien Conspiracy Investigation Agency" and the "Spirit Investigation Agency" in Moon City, and began a bizarre and funny experience. 　　 Finally, with the help of humans, the space mouse captured all the prisoners. In Jiming Town, a group of hospitable residents are performing fun stories every day . It is indeed an animated series with quite Chinese characteristics. 　　 The widower Boss Zheng, who is nearly 40 years old, studied in a private school. Boss Zheng and his fellow six men barely supported the business of the inn. The 30-year-old Azhen's wife is a widow, with a bright and sharp personality, and a good fist, she brought her helper Xiaocui to manage the bun shop prosperously. He has a personality like an old urchin, and he is rarely sober all day long, but he is a very prestigious and important person in the town. Grandpa Jiu often becomes the object of competition between Boss Zheng and A-Zhen. Sometimes, Grandpa Jiu is a peacemaker and a referee... In the conflicts, people in the small town gradually learned to tolerate each other, and finally lived happily and happily. (translated from douban)

One day, the Martian wizard "decimal point" was also locked in and locked by a mathematical code, unable to turn on the magical energy. (translated from acfun)

title: Qihuan Ya Xian Bao
synopsis: Pippi's mother is a dentist, and a fairy tale book about the legend of the tooth fairy left by his father influenced Pippi to believe in the existence of the tooth fairy. Pippi told his classmates the story of the tooth fairy but was ridiculed by his classmates, so Pippi decided to catch a tooth fairy to prove it. In the evening, Pippi finally waited for the sweet tooth fairy to arrive, but in the process of capturing it, he crossed to the tooth fairy castle where the tooth fairy lived. (translated from baidu baike)

title: Dream of the Red Chamber (2011)
synopsis: The four families of Jinling were married and joined together, and they were all damaged and all prosperous. Jia Baoyu came into the world with precious jade in his mouth, and was born smart. He also has several uncles or half-sisters who welcome spring, cherish spring, and Tanchun grow up with Baoyu, read and play. After Baoyu's aunt Jia Min died, his grandmother took Lin Daiyu into Jia's residence. Although Daiyu was young, she behaved well. Then Xue Baochai lived in Lixiangyuan, and after the main characters appeared on the stage, the story started from Grandma Liu's first entry to Rongguo Mansion and ends with Grandma Liu's third entry to Rongguo Mansion. During this period, through different winds and rains, the fate of several protagonists also fluctuated with the rise and fall of Jia's house.(translated from baidu baike)

title: Dream of the Red Chamber (2018)
synopsis: This film uses some classic plots with lively and funny cartoon animations to make children feel like they are in the story scene. Each short story is short, exciting, interesting, and profound. It is suitable for children to watch and learn. Watching cartoons and listening to stories can attract children's attention, thereby fostering children's interest in traditional classics and absorbing the essence of precious classics. (translated from iqiyi)

title: Xiao Xiao Lushi
synopsis: In this era of rapid development, people must not only bathe in all the joy of sunshine, but also face all the gloom and haze. The young people who grow up in this era are lucky, but they will also encounter many problems in school, family and society. For legal-related issues, they often feel confused and helpless because of this, and do not know how to solve them. Through animation, young people can enhance their legal awareness and develop the habit of using the law to solve problems. Huo Jie is a 12-year-old boy who is influenced by his family. He has strong logical reasoning ability and rich legal knowledge. When encountering relevant problems in life, he can always find the correct answer at the critical moment. , So everyone is called "little lawyer". The film takes Huo Jie as the main line, uses lively forms of expression, entertaining and subtly educating young people on the legal system. (translated from baidu baike)

title: Mai Jieke Xiao Zhen
synopsis: "McJack Town" is a cartoon idol music growth show with fresh original music, interesting plot, excellent aesthetics and happy emotional intelligence. "Magic Town", a homophonic from Magic Town. Just like the literal meaning of "magic town", it symbolizes the children's world full of unlimited imagination like magic. While inspiring children's imagination, it also cultivates children's EQ wisdom through interesting stories between town residents . (translated from douban)

title: Jinxiu Shenzhou Zhi Qi You Ji
synopsis: According to legend, the seven ancient artifacts were infinitely powerful, and the Black Xuanwu wanted to take them as his own and realized the ulterior conspiracy, and sent people to forcibly unblock the Kaitian Beast. After a great battle in Shenyi Village, the old patriarch died and the stone had to be left to guard the village, while Panzheng worshipped the Suzaku Xingjun to practice martial arts, and was involved in the struggle for artifacts. Under the guidance of Suzaku Xingjun, in order to crush the conspiracy of the evil forces, Panzheng went to the Yandi Mausoleum to find the Pangu key. He accidentally opened the Pangu key and came to this world through thousands of years. Together with many like-minded partners, he embarked on a journey to China. And an adventure to find artifacts.(translated from baidu baike)

title: Jinxiu Shenzhou Zhi Xingshi Wangguo
synopsis: In ancient times, on the land of China, the eight kingdoms named Ji, Ying, Jiang, Yao, Si, 妘, 姞, and 妫 were gathered by surnames. There are imperial spiritual masters all over the land of Shenzhou. They use lanterns with their surnames as the medium to summon guardian spirits of different attributes, thus possessing the power to overwhelm the river and the sea. It is the dream of all the guardian spirits to become the strongest guardian spirit master bred in the tree of surnames through layers of tests! The ordinary boy without a surname in Sunny, accidentally obtained a powerful guardian spirit with the most special lantern without a surname. Since then, he has been accidentally and thrilled, and embarked on a wonderful journey of collecting surname fire with his friends. The adventure is full of thrills but full of laughter. A seemingly impossible task has unexpected results. versus(translated from iqiyi)

title: Cike Nieyinniang Qianchuan
synopsis: The sky is high in wind and the grass is long and wild. During the Zhenguan period of the Tang Dynasty, the daughter of Nie Feng’s daughter Nie Yinniang and her cousin Tian Ji’an from Weibofan Township had no guesses. Who ever wanted to be taken abducted by a Taoist aunt when she was ten years old. As the opponent's disciple, Yinniang is studying martial arts in the isolated mountains. Three years have passed in the blink of an eye. At this time, Yinniang is as light as the wind. She jumped to the top at a swift speed. With a light flick, the sword accurately pierced the eagle flying above the sky. But facing the chicks waiting to be fed, she still didn't seem to cut her compassion. Two years have passed in a blink of an eye. In the bamboo forest full of moonlight, the master and disciples covered their eyes with cloth and drew their swords for a duel. This is Yinniang's trial of becoming a teacher, but it is also the beginning of a long and painful road... (translated from douban)

title: Ti Ke Chunji Pian
synopsis: In summer, the children of the human world became the new masters of the peerless artifact "Dragon Map" by mistake, thus entering a world where spirit, man, and devil were mixed. To help Kunlun messenger TICO, summer and his friends rushed to the spiritual world. Participate in the martial arts contest held by the spirit world, and take advantage of this to subdue 24 guardian spirits, and the devil world is also eyeing for this, and the dark school envoys participate in it. The guardian spirit of the twenty-four solar terms, and the little masters who fight for faith and justice, waiting for them will be the four elders in the Xuantian Capital, or the mysterious power hidden in the dark, a game that cannot be missed The mysterious and thrilling journey has officially begun...(translated from douban)

title: Ti Ke Zhi Shuqi De Weiji
synopsis: In a war-torn alien world, a spaceship escaped from the pursuit and departed at high speed. At the far end of the galaxy, Ah Chunzheng, a talented young inventor on Earth, is living a carefree campus life with a group of friends. When Ah Chun returned home at night, the home-made flying saucer detector suddenly alarmed. Ah Chun excitedly invited his buddy Lingzi to the outskirts to look for the fallen flying saucer. Next to a large pit burning with flames, Ah Chun found the biggest discovery in his life-an escape capsule equipped with aliens... (translated from douban)

title: Ti Ke Xiaji Pian
synopsis: "In the sweltering summer, in order to rescue the Nuwa tribesmen who were captured by Luo Xuan, Xia Tian, Tico, Peng Peng, and Kros embarked on a new journey to conquer the magic palace. The four experienced difficulties through the gate of space and finally set foot on the shadow continent The land, head towards the magic palace. However, the peculiar geographic environment and weird biological populations of the Shadow Continent all become a stumbling block to the advancement of summer and the group. The three kings under Luo Xuan's seat frequently used insidious tricks to create There are many dangers. With the gradual deepening of summer and his partners, the sinister plan that Luo Xuan has been secretly brewing has also begun to surface. The ancient hatred and the present hatred, justice and conspiracy, only wait for the summer solstice, a split duel..."(translated from douban)

title: Ti Ke Dongji Pian
synopsis: The story mainly tells the young magician Ti Ke, who was born on Kunlun Star, came to the earth with a dragon map alone, hoping to conquer the guardian spirit of the 24 solar terms and save the crisis in his hometown. Under the circumstances, Longtu fell into the hands of the little earth boy Xia Xia and admitted that he was the master. In the process of subduing the guardian spirit, all kinds of enemies or friends have appeared on the stage. Tick and Xia met many friends and encountered many setbacks. At the same time, the astonishing truth hidden in the dragon map began to emerge gradually. (translated from douban)

title: Ti Ke Jiang Gushi
synopsis: "Tick Tells Stories" is a series of cartoons that reflect the noble moral sentiments of some famous people in ancient and modern my country. Each episode tells a character. Some of the characters in the story are witty, some studious, some brave, some integrity, some filial piety, some kindness and love, and some have made great contributions to the liberation and freedom of New China. Most of the stories are derived from the stories and legends of real characters. They have a sense of reality and credibility, allowing the audience to understand the traditional Chinese virtues of benevolence, justice, courtesy, wisdom, faith, loyalty, filial piety, integrity, and courage. The good qualities that should be possessed to motivate and perfect one's personality.(trasnalted from youku)

At this time, the queen told the little princess that there is a China in the east of the earth, and the singing of Chinese children is the source of the magic of goodness. The queen asked her magic guard to protect the magic kingdom for 7 days. She and the princess rode a flying horse to China. On the way, the Aba witch came and he wanted to prevent the queen from going to China. The Aba witch killed the queen. Before the queen died, she gave the magic box to the princess and asked the princess to go to China... (translated from douban)

title: Meng Zhou Tian Qing Chuanqi
synopsis: In order to rescue the dad trapped in Dreamboat World, Su Linna, Twist 01 and Lele Xiong embark on an adventure to rescue Professor Su. Su Linna learned that only by helping players of various dynasties complete their missions and finding the source code can the trapped Professor Su be rescued. Lelexiong discovered that the second player was in the Zhou Dynasty, and Twist 01 and Su Linna went to Hokyo, the capital of the Great Zhou Kingdom, which became the stage of a new legend. In order to save her father, Su Linna uses the fire feather donated by Suzaku to find Xiao Rong, who wants to become a musician, shoulders the mission of finding the heavenly chime and choreographing six dances. Professor Su discovered that Su Linna had entered Mengzhou again. He was infinitely worried. He brought his assistants Abao and Agan to the world of Mengzhou to protect her. Su Linna wittily helped Xiao Rong pass the review by the musician and promised to help him... (translated from douban)
